            <div class="panel panel-success">
                <div class="panel-heading"><strong>About PikYak...</strong></div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <!--Button group collapsable-->
                    <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                            <div class="panel-heading hightlight">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">

                                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1">
                                         What is PikYak?
                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p> An application dedicated to spreading kindess through anonymous sharing!</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2">
                                        Why was PikYak created?
                                        
                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p>The members that created this application saw a need for a way to shine a positive light on others.</p>
                                    <p>With this application this creates an easy outlet to uplift those who need encouragement.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse3">
                                         What is a "Yak"?
                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p> A "Yak" is message posted to PikYak that in its entirety is a positive message. </p>
                                    <p>A message should be intended to be kind and encouraging about whatever the topic may be.</p>
                                    <p>
                                        These messages should be a shining light to the world that connects users together through positive encouragement.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

